snippet.title: "It's Horrible" Patrick Wilson's Reaction to Working with Amber Heard(VIDEO)
snippet.description:
"It's Horrible" Patrick Wilson's Reaction to Working with Amber Heard(VIDEO) 
In this video, Film Streak showcases what we think that Patrick Wilson thinks of working with Amber Heard. This is nothing personal but we think he should be kinda annoyed with the fact that the movie may end up failing because of her.

We´ll also make sure to keep you updated on the newest movie updates and releases – so if you are interested in anything that happens in Hollywood, you should make sure to stay tuned!
